{"tid":1685542,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"<打氣post> 藍絲嘅民意: 幾時會完?","createTime":"2019-10-31T15:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:53:08.000Z","uid":223006,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe343a4d3e9e59e230199fc1eee3d5a5e758cc3","tid":1685542,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"其實大家生活中有收成期式嘅藍絲喺身邊，聽得最多佢地問嘅問題，應該係到底依家嘅情況<br />\n<strong>幾時會完; </strong> <br />\n<br />\n係，其實好多人只係會關心幾時會完等佢地嘅生活回復正常，而唔太會認真關心場運動係點完，完左有啲咩人咩勢力會收皮 等等，甚至如果清算到黑警而係可以快啲令場運動完(喺佢地眼中)，其實佢地都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地要嘅就係一種俾收成期藍絲覺得我地係打不死嘅強勢; 只有我地係打不死，冇立場嘅佢地先會覺得清算黑警反而係一個更快令場運動完嘅方式!!<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家真係唔好放棄<br />\n11.2 要喺維園見到大家!!!"},{"pid":"0b6d8b446e211cb13f1d10855ae6fa2790deb84f","tid":1685542,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:09:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df76a29f70e60dd6f885aa43c6a5d65d83c6e10","tid":1685542,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:09:24.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"4b8b721f0d7590e2769c0a6b7488e3d819cca01c","tid":1685542,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8abf441fabbf7e2e072611ca0f7d72503842c0e1","tid":1685542,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"推園見"},{"pid":"a0b9ff4e8e7fb80ee3c1a322ec397191ab6cfd0a","tid":1685542,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaee2b6377ec5326a89a07ded763cb7ff1554374","tid":1685542,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92e99aa312c040ed3f7d66ea02b595a63c5a5cb0","tid":1685542,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"同黑警鬥長命"},{"pid":"83db31dfdc69f84e1f1569427dc537115be05f76","tid":1685542,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"